00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:27.000
She actually started out as a domestic worker here in Jackson, Missouri, Marrett and her first half. She was a homeowner, became a homeowner here.

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:38.000
She did like that. That was liberating for her. It was liberating for Herbicus and actually landed in her position of being one of the terms of local business women.

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:45.000
So she ran a mom and a popsicle, a mom and a popsicle and turned it into a boom and be in this year in Jackson.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:50.000
What was it like for you? What old were you when you moved to Jackson?

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:59.000
My take was about 12 out between 15. I went back and went back and went back to that period.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:01.000
You were around very early teen years.

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:04.000
